  "title": "Revisiting the mortality of France and Italy with the multiple-cause-of-death approach",
  "abstract": "In this paper, we use the multiple cause-of-death approach to compare the mortality profiles of France and Italy in 2003. Our analysis leads to a substantial re-evaluation of the role played by certain conditions in the process leading to death. Regard",
